{"type": "game", "name": "Tharsis", "steam_appid": 323060, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "A mysterious signal originating from the Tharsis region of Mars set us on a frantic mission. Who sent it? And why? Impossible questions, but in them lie the key to humanity\u2019s survival.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow, millions of miles away from home, a micrometeoroid storm has left us with a severely damaged ship, two deceased crew, and the sneaking suspicion this trip was doomed from the start.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTharsis is a turn-based space strategy game. With dice. And cannibalism. It puts you in control of humanity\u2019s first mission to Mars, just as it\u2019s struck by a micrometeoroid storm. You must guide your crew through disasters, food shortages,  and the unforgiving nature of space \u2014 all while maintaining your sanity amidst cryptic signals and warnings from Mars.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDefy the odds, make the difficult decisions, and embark on the most important mission in human history.", "about_the_game": "A mysterious signal originating from the Tharsis region of Mars set us on a frantic mission. Who sent it? And why? Impossible questions, but in them lie the key to humanity\u2019s survival.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow, millions of miles away from home, a micrometeoroid storm has left us with a severely damaged ship, two deceased crew, and the sneaking suspicion this trip was doomed from the start.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTharsis is a turn-based space strategy game. With dice. And cannibalism. It puts you in control of humanity\u2019s first mission to Mars, just as it\u2019s struck by a micrometeoroid storm. You must guide your crew through disasters, food shortages,  and the unforgiving nature of space \u2014 all while maintaining your sanity amidst cryptic signals and warnings from Mars.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDefy the odds, make the difficult decisions, and embark on the most important mission in human history.", "short_description": "Succeedi